<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Segurotoy · Prototipo flujo WhatsApp</title>
<style>
  * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
  body {
    font-family: -apple-system, "Segoe UI", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
    background: #1c1e21;
    min-height: 100vh;
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 32px;
    padding: 32px 16px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  /* ---------- Panel lateral de control ---------- */
  .panel {
    width: 300px;
    background: #26292e;
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 20px;
    color: #d7dade;
  }
  .panel h1 { font-size: 17px; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 4px; color: #fff; }
  .panel p  { font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.5; color: #9aa0a8; margin-bottom: 16px; }
  .panel button {
    width: 100%;
    padding: 10px;
    border: none;
    border-radius: 8px;
    background: #128C7E;
    color: #fff;
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 600;
    cursor: pointer;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }
  .panel button:hover { background: #0e7265; }
  .panel .ruta {
    font-size: 12px;
    background: #1c1e21;
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 10px;
    color: #8ecfc4;
    min-height: 60px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    word-break: break-word;
  }
  .panel .ruta-label { font-size: 11px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: .5px; color: #6b7178; margin: 14px 0 6px; }

  /* ---------- iPhone ---------- */
  .iphone {
    width: 375px;
    background: #000;
    border-radius: 52px;
    padding: 12px;
    box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0,0,0,.5);
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .pantalla {
    background: #ECE5DD;
    border-radius: 42px;
    overflow: hidden;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    height: 740px;
    position: relative;
  }

  /* Header de WhatsApp */
  .wa-header { background: #075E54; color: #fff; padding: 12px 14px 10px; flex-shrink: 0; }
  .isla { width: 118px; height: 30px; background: #000; border-radius: 16px; margin: 0 auto 10px; }
  .wa-header-fila { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; }
  .avatar {
    width: 38px; height: 38px; border-radius: 50%;
    background: #25D366;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    font-size: 20px;
  }
  .wa-nombre { flex: 1; }
  .wa-nombre b { font-size: 16px; font-weight: 600; display: block; }
  .wa-nombre span { font-size: 12px; color: #B2DFDB; }
  .wa-iconos { display: flex; gap: 18px; font-size: 18px; }

  /* Chat */
  .chat {
    flex: 1;
    overflow-y: auto;
    padding: 12px 12px 8px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 8px;
    background-image:
      radial-gradient(circle at 25% 25%, rgba(0,0,0,.015) 2px, transparent 2px),
      radial-gradient(circle at 75% 75%, rgba(0,0,0,.015) 2px, transparent 2px);
    background-size: 60px 60px;
  }
  .chip {
    align-self: center;
    background: #D4E7F5;
    color: #3a5266;
    font-size: 11px;
    padding: 4px 10px;
    border-radius: 8px;
  }
  .chip.cifrado { background: #FCF3CF; color: #6b5d1f; max-width: 260px; text-align: center; padding: 6px 10px; }

  .burbuja {
    max-width: 82%;
    padding: 7px 9px 5px;
    font-size: 14px;
    line-height: 1.45;
    color: #111;
    position: relative;
    animation: entrar .18s ease-out;
  }
  @keyframes entrar { from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(6px); } to { opacity: 1; transform: none; } }
  .bot {
    align-self: flex-start;
    background: #fff;
    border-radius: 0 10px 10px 10px;
    box-shadow: 0 1px 1px rgba(0,0,0,.08);
  }
  .usuario {
    align-self: flex-end;
    background: #DCF8C6;
    border-radius: 10px 0 10px 10px;
    box-shadow: 0 1px 1px rgba(0,0,0,.08);
  }
  .hora { font-size: 10.5px; color: #8a8a8a; text-align: right; margin-top: 3px; }
  .usuario .hora { color: #7a9c6d; }
  .check { color: #4FC3F7; }

  /* Menú de opciones (list message / quick replies) */
  .menu {
    align-self: flex-start;
    background: #fff;
    border-radius: 10px;
    width: 82%;
    box-shadow: 0 1px 1px rgba(0,0,0,.08);
    overflow: hidden;
    animation: entrar .18s ease-out;
  }
  .menu-titulo { font-size: 13.5px; color: #111; padding: 8px 10px; }
  .opcion {
    border-top: 0.5px solid #e4e4e4;
    padding: 11px 8px;
    font-size: 14px;
    color: #00796B;
    text-align: center;
    font-weight: 500;
    cursor: pointer;
    user-select: none;
    transition: background .12s;
  }
  .opcion:hover { background: #f2faf8; }
  .opcion:active { background: #d8f0ea; }
  .opcion.desactivada { pointer-events: none; opacity: .45; }

  /* Escribiendo... */
  .escribiendo {
    align-self: flex-start;
    background: #fff;
    border-radius: 0 10px 10px 10px;
    padding: 12px 14px;
    display: flex; gap: 4px;
    box-shadow: 0 1px 1px rgba(0,0,0,.08);
  }
  .escribiendo i {
    width: 7px; height: 7px; border-radius: 50%;
    background: #b0b0b0;
    animation: puntito 1.2s infinite;
  }
  .escribiendo i:nth-child(2) { animation-delay: .2s; }
  .escribiendo i:nth-child(3) { animation-delay: .4s; }
  @keyframes puntito { 0%,60%,100% { transform: none; opacity:.5; } 30% { transform: translateY(-4px); opacity:1; } }

  /* Barra inferior */
  .wa-input { background: #F0F0F0; padding: 8px 10px 6px; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; flex-shrink: 0; }
  .wa-input .campo {
    flex: 1;
    background: #fff;
    border-radius: 18px;
    padding: 9px 12px;
    font-size: 13.5px;
    color: #9a9a9a;
  }
  .wa-input .icono { font-size: 20px; color: #54656F; }
  .home-bar { background: #F0F0F0; display: flex; justify-content: center; padding: 4px 0 10px; }
  .home-bar div { width: 130px; height: 5px; background: #000; border-radius: 5px; }

  @media (max-width: 800px) {
    body { padding: 0; gap: 0; background: #000; }
    .panel { display: none; }
    .iphone { width: 100%; max-width: 420px; border-radius: 0; padding: 0; box-shadow: none; }
    .pantalla { border-radius: 0; height: 100dvh; }
    .isla { display: none; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

  <!-- Panel de control -->
  <div class="panel">
    <h1>Segurotoy · Prototipo</h1>
    <p>Toca las opciones dentro del teléfono para navegar el flujo. Algunos pasos se reproducen solos (respuestas simuladas del cliente). Todo está definido en el objeto <b>FLUJO</b> del código.</p>
    <button onclick="reiniciar()">↺ Reiniciar flujo</button>
    <div class="ruta-label">Ruta recorrida</div>
    <div class="ruta" id="ruta">inicio</div>
  </div>

  <!-- iPhone -->
  <div class="iphone">
    <div class="pantalla">
      <div class="wa-header">
        <div class="isla"></div>
        <div class="wa-header-fila">
          <span style="font-size:22px;">‹</span>
          <div class="avatar">🛡️</div>
          <div class="wa-nombre">
            <b>Segurotoy</b>
            <span id="estado">en línea</span>
          </div>
          <div class="wa-iconos"><span>📹</span><span>📞</span></div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="chat" id="chat"></div>

      <div class="wa-input">
        <span class="icono">＋</span>
        <div class="campo">Mensaje</div>
        <span class="icono">📷</span>
        <span class="icono">🎤</span>
      </div>
      <div class="home-bar"><div></div></div>
    </div>
  </div>

<script>
/* =====================================================
   FLUJO DE CONVERSACIÓN — edita aquí
   Cada nodo tiene:
   - mensajes: array de textos que envía el bot
   - menu: { titulo, opciones: [{ etiqueta, destino }] }
   - fin: true si el nodo cierra la conversación
